==Symmetry==
The dual to this tiling represents the fundamental domains of *∞2∞2 symmetry group. The symmetry can be doubled by adding mirrors on either diagonal of the rhombic domains, creating [[ii2 symmetry|*∞∞2]] and [[i44 symmetry|*∞44 symmetry]].

